NAME		siteban
SYNTAX		siteban [<host> <level>]
DESCRIPTION	Set a lockout on a particular host or group of hosts.
		[host] can include an asterix ie.. to ban Leeds, use
			siteban 129.11.* 1
		or
			siteban leeds 1
		Available levels may change - to get the current list, just
		type 'siteban levels'. At the time of writing, the levels
		are:
			    Ban all:           1
			    Ban all but admin: 2
			    Ban all newbies:   3

		Siteban with no arguments just lists banned sites.
